.body-wrap
.site-wrapper
  .site-wrapper-inner
    .cover-container
      .masthead.clearfix
        .inner
          %h3.masthead-brand= image_tag('wingman-white.png')
          %ul.nav.masthead-nav
            %li.active
              %a{href: "#"} Home
            %li
              %a{href: "#features"} Features
            %li
              %a{href: "#"} Contact
      .inner.cover
        #main-cover
          %h1.cover-heading Introducing WingMan
          %p.lead WingMan gives you the ultimate control of your night life. Whether you’re looking to recreate your own scene from “The Hangover”, or just spend a relaxing night out on the town . . WingMan's got your back!
          %p.lead
            %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-default{href: "#features"} Interested yet?
.background
  #features.container.marketing
    / Main component for a primary marketing message or call to action
    / Three columns of text below the carousel
    .row
      #market1.col-lg-4
        %img.img-circle{alt: "stats", "src" => asset_url('stats.png')}/
        %h2 Preference Filtering
        %p WingMan personally selects venues based on your preferences, and intentions for the night. Let us know a few things about yourself… Male or female? Single, married, or swinger? Hip-Hop or Hipster? (WingMan doesn’t judge!)
      / /.col-lg-4
      #market2.col-lg-4
        %img.img-circle{alt: "location", "src" => asset_url('location.png')}/
        %h2 Location, Location, Location!
        %p How far are you willing to travel? Whether it’s a couple blocks away… or a couple cities, WingMan only suggests venues based on your traveling preferences. Need directions? Don’t sweat it – WingMan will directly connect you to a mapping service with just a tap of your finger.
      / /.col-lg-4
      #market3.col-lg-4
        %img.img-circle{alt: "social", "src" => asset_url('browser.png')}/
        %h2 Social Savvy
        %p WingMan knows you’re pretty popular on the Internet… and you’re probably not interested in seeing all 1,000+ of your Facebook friend’s locations on your phone… That’s why WingMan has incorporated the revolutionary ability to prioritize your closest friends over acquaintances when mapping their locations. 
      / /.col-lg-4
    / /.row

.container.quick-slogan
  .row
    .col-lg-12
      %h1.cover-heading.font-anim The Perfect Night Every Night

    / START THE FEATURETTES
.background
  #features.container.marketing
    .row.featurette
      #mock1-text.col-md-7.featurette-text
        %h2.featurette-heading
          In the Loop.
          %span.text-muted From the Start.
        %p.lead WingMan connects with your favorite social networking sites to take ‘Facebook stalking’ to a whole new level! …Just kidding… WingMan does, however, map the location of all your best buds using WingMan’s location services. If a friend checks into a location using one of the many social networking sites WingMan supports, you’ll have the ability to keep tabs on all of the popular venues your friends have been checking out! 
      .col-md-5
        %img#mock1.featurette-image.img-responsive{alt: "mockup 1", "src" => asset_url('wingman1.png')}/
    %hr.featurette-divider/
    .row.featurette
      .col-md-5
        %img#mock2.featurette-image.img-responsive{alt: "mockup 2", "src" => asset_url('iphonelogin.png')}/
      #mock2-text.col-md-7.featurette-text
        %h2.featurette-heading
          It’s all about the 
          %span.text-muted Atmosphere...
        %p.lead Sometimes, it’s a little hard to vibe a place out just by reading its name…  “Dirty Dick’s” can mean a WHOLE lot of things. WingMan gets straight to the point. We’ll let you know the theme of the venue, the music it plays, food/drinks it serves, and all of the ratings and opinions provided by the experienced bar-goers in your community. 
